ZH: 我喜欢在晚餐时喝一杯红葡萄酒。
EN: I like to drink a glass of red wine with dinner.

ZH: 这瓶葡萄酒的味道很浓郁。
EN: This bottle of wine has a rich flavor.

ZH: 他们在庆祝生日的时候开了一瓶好葡萄酒。
EN: They opened a nice bottle of wine to celebrate their birthday.

ZH: 一杯白葡萄酒很适合搭配海鲜料理。
EN: A glass of white wine pairs well with seafood dishes.

ZH: 她为客人准备了一些干白葡萄酒。
EN: She prepared some dry white wine for the guests.

ZH: 这家餐馆有各种葡萄酒可供选择。
EN: This restaurant has a variety of wines to choose from.

