EN: This glass of sweet wine has a hint of rose fragrance.

ZH: 他在生日宴会上得到了一瓶贵族级的葡萄酒。
EN: He received a bottle of premium wine at his birthday party.

ZH: 做一盘意大利面配上一杯红葡萄酒，会很赞。
EN: Making a plate of pasta paired with a glass of red wine would be wonderful.

ZH: 昨晚我喝了一些玫瑰葡萄酒，感觉非常放松。
EN: I drank some rose wine last night and felt very relaxed.

ZH: 他建议把葡萄酒醒一下再喝，这样味道会更好。
